ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.ast

接口 ASTHelper<T extends StructureNode>

  • 类型参数:
    T - subtype of StructureNode with which the AST helper works
    所有已知实现类:
    JavaASTHelper

    public interface ASTHelper<T extends StructureNode>
    Handles language specific ASTs and provides access to their content. An AST helper is associated to a file.
    作者:
    Beat Fluri, Giacomo Ghezzi

    • 方法概要

      • createMethodInClassHistory

        StructureEntityVersion createMethodInClassHistory(ClassHistory classHistory,
                                                  T node,
                                                  String version)
        Creates and returns the StructureEntityVersion as method of the ClassHistory. The method is attached to the corresponding MethodHistory, if exists. Otherwise a new one is created.
        参数:
        classHistory - to create the structure entity version for
        node - to create the structure entity version
        version - the number or id of the version to create
        返回:
        the method structure entity version in the class history for the node
